  "body": "Versions: \r\n```\r\n\"@nomicfoundation/hardhat-chai-matchers\": \"^1.0.4\",\r\n\"hardhat\": \"^2.12.2\",\r\n\"@types/chai\": \"^4.3.4\",\r\n\"chai\": \"^4.3.7\",\r\n\"chai-ethers\": \"^0.0.1\",\r\n```\r\n\r\nNote that I think that there are issues with types as a result of having both of these and they interfere with each other. The solution for me was to simply remove:\r\n\r\n```\r\n\"@types/chai\": \"^4.3.4\",\r\n\"chai\": \"^4.3.7\",\r\n\"chai-ethers\": \"^0.0.1\",\r\n```",
